# Web UI Testing

## Description

This educational project was completed as part of the QA Engineer program at Yandex Practicum.

This project demonstrates web UI testing, checklist creation, test case design, bug reporting, cross-browser testing, and testing on different screen resolutions.

## Objective

The objective of this project was to verify the user interface, validate application functionality, identify visual and functional defects, and document testing results.

## What I did

- Created UI testing checklists.
- Tested page layout and interface elements.
- Designed test cases for booking functionality.
- Performed cross-browser testing.
- Verified application behavior on different screen resolutions.
- Reported and documented defects.
- Linked checklists and test cases to related bug reports.

